Our family favorites such as Maggi, Bear Brand, and Cerevita are at the forefront of delivering fortified servings of food and beverages. In 2020 alone, we're talking 196.6 billion servings! 🥗 

Visit the link in our bio to find out more ⬆️ 

#GenerationRegeneration​​

Guys disintegratable plastics exist. Check out solutum.co and partner up 

You have done this much damage, now be the hero and clean it up and prevent it in the future. You can win back the hearts (and $$$) of millions. 🙏 ❤️
